officialTitle: Pelvic Floor Muscle Evaluation in Women With Stress Urinary and Urgency Urinary Incontinence. A Prospective Trial
inclusionCriteria:
* presence of stress urinary or urgency incontinence
* Must be FEMALE
* Must have minimum age of 18 Years
* Must have maximum age of 65 Years
exclusionCriteria:
* neurological diseases
* previous pelvic surgeries
* diabetes
* cognitive difficulties
* vaginal and urinary infection
